text: Jusuf Gazibegović (born 11 March 2000) is a Bosnian football player. He plays for SK Sturm Graz in the Austrian Football Bundesliga as a defender. ==Career== Gazibegovic started in the youth teams of Red Bull Salzburg. Then he went on to the football academy of FC Red Bull Salzburg from 2016 to 2018. He also played for the UEFA Youth League squad in 2017–18. There he scored one goal against Girondis Bordeaux.
